<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex">
  <title>Something went wrong — Bench Review</title>
  <style>
    :root { color-scheme: light; }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #111827;
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .card {
      max-width: 28rem;
      margin: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .code { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; }
    h1 { margin: 0.75rem 0 0; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; }
    p { margin: 0.75rem 0 0; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #4b5563; }
    a.btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1.75rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.1rem;
      background: #111827;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }
    a.btn:hover { background: #374151; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="card">
    <p class="code">500</p>
    <h1>Something went wrong on our end</h1>
    <p>We hit an unexpected error while loading this page. It's not you — it's us. Please try again in a moment.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="/">Go back home</a>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
